    excerpt: 'Learn damage-free furniture anchoring techniques perfect for rental apartments. Child-proof your home without wall damage or losing your security deposit.',
    metaDescription: 'Learn damage-free furniture anchoring techniques perfect for rental apartments. Child-proof your home without wall damage or losing your security deposit.',
