    slug: 'empowering-preteens-advanced-kitchen-safety-culinary-independence',
    title: 'Empowering Pre-Teens with Advanced Kitchen Safety Skills: A Parent\'s Guide to Fostering Culinary Independence',
    category: 'Food Safety',
    excerpt: 'Guide parents in teaching pre-teens advanced kitchen safety, from knife skills to stove use. Foster culinary independence safely and confidently.',
    metaDescription: 'Guide parents in teaching pre-teens advanced kitchen safety, from knife skills to stove use. Foster culinary independence safely and confidently.',
